{"artist":null,"title":"From Silence To Sorcery","resource_url":"https://api.discogs.com/releases/1081672","year":"2007","notes":"Released as thirteenth CD in Zorn's <i>Composer Series</i>.\r\n\r\n<i>Goetia</i> composed in 2002, <i>Gris-Gris</i> in 2000, and <i>Shibboleth</i> in 1997.\r\n\r\n<i>Shibboleth</i> is divided into six parts:\r\n\r\ni Abglanzbeladen (Laden With Reflection)\r\nii Im Leeren (In Empty Space)\r\niii Mandelnde (Almond-Like)\r\niv Hinterlassne (Left Back)\r\nv Etwas Wie Nacht (Something Like Night)\r\nvi Aus Verlorem (From Things Lost)\r\n\r\n<i>(The correct German name of vi is \"Aus Verlorenem\".)</i>\r\n\r\nRecorded, mixed and edited 2005 and 2007 at Avatar, Hit Factory and Legacy Sound.\r\n\r\nBarcode on Tzadik strip: 7 02397-8035-2 2\r\n\r\nCD matrix: TZACD8035 1N 01\r\nIFPI L250\r\nIFPI 4160\r\n\r\nA Project of Hips Road\r\n(c)(p) 2007 Tzadik, 200 East 10th Street, pmb 126, New York, NY 10003\r\n","uri":"https://www.discogs.com/John-Zorn-From-Silence-To-Sorcery/release/1081672","images":[{"uri":"https://img.discogs.com/334oWHzGtNpa-odrxI5j4qt8ooo=/fit-in/600x609/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(90)/discogs-images/R-1081672-1200703211.jpeg.jpg","uri150":"https://img.discogs.com/G4xWktTWBRLK3XsqiVHBJIekl4s=/fit-in/150x150/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(40)/discogs-images/R-1081672-1200703211.jpeg.jpg","height":609,"width":600,"type":"secondary"},{"uri":"https://img.discogs.com/4lBTI24E1JFTG5ilK2lmKZYTWuY=/fit-in/600x611/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(90)/discogs-images/R-1081672-1200703245.jpeg.jpg","uri150":"https://img.discogs.com/Lo_tdm9XAStpjFxsBOPW4kFHMyo=/fit-in/150x150/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(40)/discogs-images/R-1081672-1200703245.jpeg.jpg","height":611,"width":600,"type":"secondary"},{"uri":"https://img.discogs.com/zxcgEypNNQxGKzvAkiB2d71GvLc=/fit-in/600x617/filters:strip_icc():format(jpeg):mode_rgb():quality(90)/discogs-images/R-1081672-1200703